      "content": "That \"obsolete\" part is a pretty huge claim though. If they're so obviously bad, why do major political leaders and entire regions keep pushing for them? It feels like you're dismissing the idea that national security or bringing manufacturing back home could be valid goals. Are you saying those goals don't matter if they don't fit the standard economic model?",
